}', 'SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT a.id) AS C1, t.name as C2
FROM `threat` t
INNER JOIN `threat_to_asset_type_group` ttatgp ON ttatgp.threat_id = t.id
INNER JOIN `asset_type_group` atg ON atg.id = ttatgp.asset_type_group_id
INNER JOIN `asset_type` ast ON ast.asset_type_group_id = atg.id
INNER JOIN `asset` a ON a.`type_id` = ast.id

DATE_FORMAT(ra.modified_on,'%d/%m/%Y %H:%i') AS C3
FROM risk_assessment ra 
INNER JOIN business_service_to_risk_assessment bsra on bsra.risk_assessment_id = ra.id
INNER JOIN business_service bs on bs.id = bsra.business_service_id

 "text": "Step Interpolation"
 }
 }
 } 
} ', 'SELECT tbl.C1, tbl.C2 FROM
(SELECT DISTINCT CONCAT('(',c.code,' ',a.code,') ',t.name ) AS C1, 
ifnull((SELECT MAX(r.score_sum) FROM risk r 
 WHERE r.asset_to_composite_asset_threat_id = atcat.id 
 AND r.risk_assessment_id = ra.id),0) AS C2 
FROM risk_assessment ra 
INNER JOIN business_service_to_risk_assessment bsra on bsra.risk_assessment_id = ra.id
INNER JOIN composite_asset_to_business_service cabs on cabs.business_service_id = bsra.business_service_id
INNER JOIN asset_to_composite_asset atca on atca.composite_asset_id = cabs.composite_asset_id
INNER JOIN asset_to_composite_asset_threat atcat on atcat.asset_to_composite_asset_id = atca.id
INNER JOIN threat t ON t.id = atcat.threat_id
 INNER JOIN composite_asset c ON c.id = cabs.composite_asset_id
 INNER JOIN asset a ON a.id = atca.asset_id
WHERE bsra.id = :BSLID) tbl
WHERE C2 > 0
ORDER BY C2 DESC
', b'1', 'Composite Assets With Highest Risk Score On Assessment', 'Composite Asset Threats Contribution Towards Overall Risk'), (8, NULL, '2022-03-02 10:01:57', NULL, '2022-03-08 10:42:36', NULL, 5, NULL, NULL, 0, 'C1', 'fa-chart-pie', '{

} ', 'SELECT C1, C2 
FROM (
SELECT DISTINCT r.cve_id AS C1,
(SELECT MAX(rr.score_sum) FROM risk rr WHERE rr.id = r.id) AS C2,
r.score_sum
FROM risk r 
WHERE r.business_service_to_risk_assessment_id = :BSLID
) tbl ORDER BY tbl.score_sum DESC
LIMIT 10', b'1', 'CVEs with Highest Risk Score on Assessment', 'Vulnerability Contribution Towards Overall Risk');
